      "author": "rachelatmonday (Rachel)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>We recently held a one-day hackathon focused on quick updates based on known issues and <a href=\"https://community.monday.com/t/share-your-ux-feedback-for-the-developer-section/87186\">feedback from our community</a>. Check out what’s new below!</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/4/4/449d05d1a296683da74ca13a6b68b88e8bf2d8c8.jpeg\" title=\"Dev center improvements\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/4/4/449d05d1a296683da74ca13a6b68b88e8bf2d8c8_2_690x349.jpeg\" alt=\"Dev center improvements\" width=\"690\" height=\"349\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Dev center improvements</span><span class=\"informations\">3014×1525 351 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Personalized welcome headers with your profile name <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/wave.png?v=12\" title=\":wave:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":wave:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></li>\n<li>Search by app name to make locating your app a breeze (and it even auto-focuses on the search bar when you open the app page!) <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/mag.png?v=12\" title=\":mag:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":mag:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></li>\n<li>Open links in new tabs or windows (with a right-click) <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/window.png?v=12\" title=\":window:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":window:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></li>\n</ol>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/3/9/392575ab656a04de74d4debbc7d36227ab485a61.png\" title=\"Dev center improvements (2)\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/3/9/392575ab656a04de74d4debbc7d36227ab485a61_2_690x349.png\" alt=\"Dev center improvements (2)\" width=\"690\" height=\"349\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Dev center improvements (2)</span><span class=\"informations\">3014×1525 366 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Create a new app version or promote a draft from any page <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/boom.png?v=12\" title=\":boom:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":boom:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></li>\n<li>Search by feature name instead of scrolling through a long list (and it even auto-focuses on the search bar when you open the feature page!) <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/mag.png?v=12\" title=\":mag:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":mag:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></li>\n<li>More descriptive app feature names for <strong>new</strong> app features (e.g., Board View feature or Account Settings View feature) <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/writing_hand.png?v=12\" title=\":writing_hand:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":writing_hand:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></li>\n</ol>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/b/c/bce50cd09001cc744a32cfc32f803e2b809f86d6.png\" title=\"Dev center improvements (3)\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/b/c/bce50cd09001cc744a32cfc32f803e2b809f86d6_2_690x349.png\" alt=\"Dev center improvements (3)\" width=\"690\" height=\"349\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Dev center improvements (3)</span><span class=\"informations\">3014×1525 282 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<ol>\n<li>The left-pane menu won’t jump when you switch between tabs <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/anchor.png?v=12\" title=\":anchor:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":anchor:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></li>\n<li>Smaller header on the <em>App versions</em> tab so you have more real estate to manage versioning <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/open_file_folder.png?v=12\" title=\":open_file_folder:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":open_file_folder:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></li>\n</ol>"
    }
